  "texts": [
    "We explore a spectrum of methods for LLM-based puzzle solving, ranging from prompting techniques to neuro-symbolic strategies and fine-tuning.",
    "By collating existing datasets in this domain, we provide a comprehensive overview of the resources available for such evaluations.",
    "Our analysis identifies current challenges, revealing a difficulty of most methods to successfully solve puzzles, while we outline future directions, emphasizing the need for advanced methodologies and diverse datasets to enhance LLMs' proficiency in puzzle solving.",
    "In this study, we provide a survey of puzzle solving using reasoning of Large Language Models.",
    "Despite our best efforts, there may be still some limitations that remain in this paper."
  ],
